{{Infobox Union |name= POSTKOM |country= [[Norway]] |affiliation= [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions|LO]] |members= |full_name= Norwegian Post and Communications Union |native_name= Norsk Post og Kommunikasjonsforbund |image= [[File:POSTKOM logo.png|175px]] |founded= 2000 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Oslo]], Norway |people= [[Odd Christian Øverland]], president |website= [http://www.postkom.org www.postkom.org] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Norwegian Post and Communications Union''' (POSTKOM) is a [[trade union]] in [[Norway]]. It was formed in 2000 from the merger of the [[Norwegian Postal Organization]], and the [[Norwegian Union of Postmen]].
POSTKOM is affiliated with the [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions]] (LO).
